#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdesvn; is a <ulink url=\"http://subversion.apache.org/\">subversion "
"client</ulink> by &kde;."
msgstr ""
"&kdesvn; je <ulink url=\"http://subversion.apache.org/\">odjemalec za "
"subversion</ulink> &kde;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You should have some knowledge about subversion itself, but hopefully most "
"items are self explanatory."
msgstr ""
"Morali bi imeti nekaj znanja o samem programu subversion, vendar upajmo, da "
"je večina elementov razumljivih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may send bug reports and feature wishes via <ulink url=\"https://bugs."
"kde.org/\">&kde; Bugtracking System</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Poročila o napakah in želje po funkcijah lahko pošljete prek <ulink url="
"\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde; Sistem za sledenje napakam</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terms"
msgstr "Pogoji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you're familiar with revision control systems you may skip that - or read "
"and correct the author ;)"
msgstr ""
"Če ste seznanjeni s sistemi za nadzor revizij, lahko to preskočite - ali "
"preberete in popravite avtorja ;)"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Repository</term>"
msgstr "<term>Repozitorij</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Central store of data. That may be a database or a flat filesystem. Without "
"special clients you're not able to read data in it. For Subversion "
"repositories &kdesvn; is such a client."
msgstr ""
"Centralna shramba podatkov. To je lahko baza podatkov ali ploski datotečni "
"sistem. Brez posebnih odjemalcev ne morete brati podatkov v njem. Za "
"repozitorije Subversion &kdesvn; je taka stranka."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Working copy</term>"
msgstr "<term>Delovna kopija</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A flat copy of a repository on local filesystem. This is used like any "
"normal filemanager, editing files and so forth. RCS-information you can read "
"with clients like &kdesvn;."
msgstr ""
"Ravna kopija repozitorija v lokalnem datotečnem sistemu. To se uporablja kot "
"vsak običajni upravljalnik datotek, urejanje datotek in tako naprej. RCS-"
"informacije, ki jih lahko preberete z odjemalci, kot je &kdesvn;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remember that subversion does not know anything about KIO, so a working copy "
"must reside in an area where it may reached without any specific protocol, "
"&eg; <quote>fish://</quote> or such is not possible."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da subversion ne ve ničesar o KIO, zato mora biti delovna "
"kopija na območju, kamor lahko doseže brez posebnega protokola, &eg; "
"<quote>fish://</quote> ali kaj takega ni mogoče."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid "WebDav"
msgstr "WebDav"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"WebDav is a protocol which let you modify files on a remote webserver. "
"Subversion is a special kind of WebDAV when repositories are accessed via "
"webserver. In normal use this is read-only. With special configurations you "
"may get a read-write enabled WebDAV which you may access via specialized "
"browser. &kdesvn; is NOT a webdav-client, but &konqueror; is via the "
"<quote>webdav://</quote> protocol. But with &kdesvn; you may browse through "
"the version tree of a repository (via <quote>http://</quote>)"
msgstr ""
"WebDav je protokol, ki vam omogoča spreminjanje datotek na oddaljenem "
"spletnem strežniku. Subversion je posebna vrsta WebDAV, ko se do "
"repozitorijev dostopa prek spletnega strežnika. Pri običajni uporabi je to "
"samo za branje. S posebnimi konfiguracijami lahko dobite WebDAV z omogočenim "
"branjem in pisanjem, do katerega lahko dostopate prek specializiranega "
"brskalnika. &kdesvn; NI odjemalec webdav, ampak &konqueror; je prek "
"protokola <quote>webdav://</quote>. Toda z &kdesvn; lahko brskate po drevesu "
"različic repozitorija (prek <quote>http://</quote>)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kdesvn;"
msgstr "Uporaba &kdesvn;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kdesvn; features"
msgstr "&kdesvn; Lastnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kdesvn; understands following protocols for browsing repositories:"
msgstr "&kdesvn; razume naslednje protokole za brskanje po repozitorijih:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "http"
msgstr "http"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard web browser protocol."
msgstr "Standardni protokol spletnega brskalnika."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "https"
msgstr "https"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Standard encrypted web browser protocol."
msgstr "Standardni šifrirani protokol spletnega brskalnika."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "(k)svn+http"
msgstr "(k)svn+http"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Standard web browser protocol. May be used to let &konqueror; automatic call "
"&kdesvn;."
msgstr ""
"Standardni protokol spletnega brskalnika. Lahko se uporablja za dovolitev "
"&konqueror; samodejni klic &kdesvn;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "(k)svn+https"
msgstr "(k)svn+https"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Standard encrypted web browser protocol. May be used to let &konqueror; "
"automatic call &kdesvn;."
msgstr ""
"Standardni šifrirani protokol spletnega brskalnika. Lahko se uporablja za "
"dovolitev &konqueror; samodejni klic &kdesvn;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "(k)svn+file"
msgstr "(k)svn+datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Local repository protocol. May be used to let &konqueror; automatic call "
"&kdesvn;."
msgstr ""
"Protokol lokalnega repozitorija. Lahko se uporablja za dovolitev &konqueror; "
"samodejni klic &kdesvn;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "(k)svn"
msgstr "(k)svn"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subversion's own server protocol."
msgstr "Lastni protokol strežnika Subversion."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "(k)svn+ssh"
msgstr "(k)svn+ssh"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "Subversion over ssh."
msgstr "Subversion nad ssh."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "file"
msgstr "mapa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Direct repository access. &kdesvn; checks if a given path is a repository or "
"a working copy and opens it in the right mode. For subversion <filename "
"class=\"directory\">file:///dir</filename> and <filename class=\"directory"
"\">/dir</filename> is not the same!"
msgstr ""
"Neposreden dostop do repozitorija. &kdesvn; preveri, ali je podana pot "
"repozitorij ali delovna kopija, in jo odpre v pravem načinu. Za subversion  "
"<filename class=\"directory\">file:///dir</filename> in <filename class="
"\"directory\">/dir</filename> nista enaka!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This list may be used for &URL;s given for <link linkend=\"kdesvn-commandline"
"\">command line</link>, too."
msgstr ""
"Ta seznam se lahko uporablja tudi za &URL;, podane za <link linkend=\"kdesvn-"
"commandline\">ukazno vrstico</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Beginning with subversion and &kdesvn;"
msgstr "Začenši s subversion in &kdesvn;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section is mostly for beginners not familiar with subversion and "
"explains how subversion and/or revision control systems (<acronym>RCS</"
"acronym>) works."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek je večinoma namenjen začetnikom, ki niso seznanjeni s programom "
"subversion, in pojasnjuje, kako delujejo subversion oz. sistemi za nadzor "
"različic (<acronym>RCS</acronym>)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating a working copy"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje delovne kopije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Working copies MUST be accessible via local paths. Subversion does not know "
"anything about pseudo file systems like <filename class=\"directory\">smb://"
"</filename> or <filename class=\"directory\">fish://</filename>. &kdesvn; "
"translates some of them if possible (like <filename class=\"directory"
"\">system:/home</filename>) but it is not possible over a network."
msgstr ""
"Delovne kopije MORAJO biti dostopne po lokalnih poteh. Subversion ne ve "
"ničesar o psevdo datotečnih sistemih, kot sta <filename class=\"directory"
"\">smb://</filename> ali <filename class=\"directory\">fish://</filename>. "
"&kdesvn; prevede nekatere od njih, če je mogoče (na primer <filename class="
"\"directory\">system:/home</filename>), vendar to ni mogoče prek omrežja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First of all you must create a working copy of your repository. For that "
"select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>General</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Checkout a repository</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. "
"Inside the following dialog you must select the &URL; of the repository you "
"want to use, &eg;, something like <literal>http://localhost/repos/myproject</"
"literal>. Subfolders of a repository are possible, too, &eg;, "
"<literal>http://localhost/repos/myproject/trunk</literal> or similar."
msgstr ""
"Najprej morate ustvariti delovno kopijo vašega repozitorija. Za to izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Splošno</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preveri repozitorij</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. V naslednjem "
"pogovornem oknu morate izbrati &URL; repozitorija, ki ga želite uporabiti, "
"&eg; nekaj takega kot <literal>http://localhost/repos/myproject</literal>. "
"Možne so tudi podmape repozitorija, npr. <literal>http://localhost/repos/"
"myproject/trunk</literal> ali podobno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select and/or create a local folder, where the working copy should reside."
msgstr "Izberite in/ali ustvarite lokalno mapo, kjer naj bo delovna kopija."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Last but not least, the revision to checkout. Mostly that should be "
"<quote>HEAD</quote>. This ensures that the last stored version is the "
"referenced version."
msgstr ""
"Nenazadnje, revizija blagajne. Večinoma bi to moralo biti <quote>GLAVA</"
"quote>. To zagotavlja, da je zadnja shranjena različica navedena različica."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After clicking on <guibutton>OK</guibutton> &kdesvn; will create your new "
"working copy and (if the box was checked) opens it."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na <guibutton>V redu</guibutton> &kdesvn; bo ustvaril vašo novo "
"delovno kopijo in (če je bilo polje označeno) jo odpre."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have opened a repository for browsing you may mark a folder and "
"than select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Repository</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Checkout current repository "
"path</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and fill out the dialogs as described "
"above. Then only the marked path will checked out."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste odprli repozitorij za brskanje, lahko označite mapo in nato izberete "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Repozitorij</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Preveri trenutno pot repozitorija</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> in izpolnite pogovorna okna, kot je opisano zgoraj. Nato bo "
"odjavljena le označena pot."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Committing local changes"
msgstr "Izvajanje lokalnih sprememb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark the entry or entries you want to send and select <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>#</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Commit</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Označite vnos ali vnose, ki jih želite poslati, in izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>#</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu > <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Potrdi</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you try to commit if no item is selected, &kdesvn; uses the top-most "
"element of opened working copy, &ie;, the working copy path itself."
msgstr ""
"Če poskusite potrditi, če ni izbran noben element, &kdesvn; uporablja "
"najvišji element odprte delovne kopije, &ie; samo pot delovne kopije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This operation is always recursive, means, if selecting a folder &kdesvn; "
"always send all changed items below it. When you setup that you want to "
"review all items before commit inside the following dialog all items "
"&kdesvn; would send are listed. There you may unmark items you don't want to "
"send. In that case &kdesvn; sends all items alone, &ie;, not recursive. Or "
"you may select items not versioned for add and commit (if them are not "
"marked to be ignored). So you may see if there are newer items you forgot."
msgstr ""
"Ta operacija je vedno rekurzivna, kar pomeni, da če izberete mapo &kdesvn; "
"vedno pošljite vse spremenjene elemente pod njim. Ko nastavite, da želite "
"pregledati vse elemente pred objavo v naslednjem pogovornem oknu, vsi "
"elementi &kdesvn; bi poslali so navedeni. Tam lahko odznačite predmete, ki "
"jih ne želite poslati. V tem primeru &kdesvn; pošlje vse elemente sam, &ie; "
"ne rekurzivno. Lahko pa izberete elemente brez različic za dodajanje in "
"objavo (če niso označeni za prezrtje). Tako boste morda videli, ali "
"obstajajo novejši predmeti, ki ste jih pozabili."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter a log message what you're sending and hit <guibutton>OK</guibutton> "
"and the transfer starts."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite dnevniško sporočilo, kaj pošiljate in pritisnite <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton> in prenos se začne."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:241
#, no-c-format
msgid "Update working copy"
msgstr "Posodobi delovno kopijo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This brings you local working copy in sync with the repository. You may "
"setup that &kdesvn; checks on opening a working copy for newer/modified "
"items in repository. This runs in background and you may work meanwhile with "
"&kdesvn;. When this is finished, items with newer versions or folders with "
"items where newer items are below are marked."
msgstr ""
"To vam prinese lokalno delovno kopijo v sinhronizacijo z repozitorijem. "
"Lahko nastavite, da &kdesvn; preverja odpiranje delovne kopije za novejše/"
"spremenjene elemente v repozitoriju. To deluje v ozadju in medtem lahko "
"delate z &kdesvn;. Ko je to končano, so označeni elementi z novejšimi "
"različicami ali mape z elementi, kjer so spodaj novejši elementi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To retrieve the changes, select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Update to head</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. This will update to the most latest version. If "
"you want to get a specific revision select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Update to "
"revision</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and select the revision you want in the "
"following box."
msgstr ""
"Če želite pridobiti spremembe, izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Posodobitev na "
"glavo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. To bo posodobilo na najnovejšo različico. "
"Če želite pridobiti določeno revizijo, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Posodobitev na revizijo</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in izberite "
"revizijo, ki jo želite v naslednje polje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no item is selected, the update will done on whole opened working copy, "
"otherwise only recursive on the selected items."
msgstr ""
"Če ni izbrana nobena postavka, bo posodobitev izvedena na celotni odprti "
"delovni kopiji, drugače pa le rekurzivno na izbranih postavkah."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding and Deleting from working copy"
msgstr "Dodajanje in brisanje iz delovne kopije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both operations requires two steps: First add or delete and then committing "
"that changes to repository. Before you commit you may undone add or delete."
msgstr ""
"Obe operaciji zahtevata dva koraka: najprej dodajanje ali brisanje in nato "
"objavo teh sprememb v repozitorij. Preden potrdite, lahko razveljavite "
"dodajanje ali brisanje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:268
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add items"
msgstr "Dodajte elemente"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding items into a working copy may be done due three ways:"
msgstr "Dodajanje elementov v delovno kopijo je mogoče na tri načine:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select not versioned items and add them"
msgstr "Izberite elemente brez različic in jih dodajte"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:274
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Copy with &konqueror; or any other tool into working copy area. Go trough "
"list, mark them and select <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Insert</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Add selected "
"files/dirs</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. When you want adding new folders "
"with all subitems select <menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Insert</keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</"
"guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Add selected "
"files/dirs recursive</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Kopiraj s &konqueror; ali katero koli drugo orodje v območje delovne kopije. "
"Pojdite skozi seznam, jih označite in izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Vstavi</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Deluje kopiraj</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj izbrane datoteke/imenike</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Ko želite dodati nove mape z vsemi podpostavkami, izberite "
"<menuchoice> <shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Vstavi</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Rekurzivno dodaj "
"izbrane datoteke/imenike</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check and add recursive"
msgstr "Preverite in dodajte rekurzivno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may check if there are somewhere in working copy unversioned items. "
"After selecting <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Check for unversioned "
"items</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> a dialog appears where all not versioned "
"items are listed. Hitting <guibutton>OK</guibutton> adds all marked items to "
"working copy, items you don't want versioned you should unmark before."
msgstr ""
"Lahko preverite, ali so kje v delovni kopiji elementi brez različic. Po "
"izbiri <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna "
"kopija</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Preveri elemente brez različic</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> se prikaže pogovorno okno, kjer so navedeni vsi "
"elementi brez različic. Če pritisnete <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>, dodate "
"vse označene elemente v delovno kopijo, elemente, za katere ne želite, da "
"imajo različico, morate prej odznačiti."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and drop"
msgstr "Povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark in &konqueror; or any other compatible file browser items you want to "
"add and drag them to &kdesvn;. You may drop them on folders inside the "
"opened working copy and then &kdesvn; copy the dropped items to it and add "
"the items."
msgstr ""
"Označi v &konqueror;ju ali katere koli druge združljive elemente brskalnika "
"datotek, ki jih želite dodati, in jih povlecite v &kdesvn;. Lahko jih "
"spustite v mape znotraj odprte delovne kopije in nato &kdesvn; vanjo "
"kopirajte izpuščene predmete in jih dodajte."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting items from working copy and unversion"
msgstr "Brisanje elementov iz delovne kopije in razveljavitev različice"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deleting items is always recursive. For example, when you delete a folder "
"all subitems will be deleted, too. Mark what you want and select "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>General</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Delete selected files/dirs</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> menu "
"item. Items will be unversioned and removed from disk."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje elementov je vedno rekurzivno. Na primer, ko izbrišete mapo, bodo "
"izbrisani tudi vsi podpostavki. Označite, kar želite, in izberite menijsko "
"postavko <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Splošno</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izbriši izbrane datoteke/imenike</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Elementi bodo brez različic in odstranjeni z diska."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displaying logs"
msgstr "Prikaz dnevnikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The log display may start with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</"
"keycap></keycombo> when one or none item is marked in overview. Depending on "
"your settings (see <xref linkend=\"subversion-settings\" xreflabel=\"settings"
"\"/>) &kdesvn; retrieves some log entries beginning on <quote>HEAD</quote> "
"and displays them."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz dnevnika se lahko začne s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</"
"keycap></keycombo>, ko je v pregledu označen en ali noben element. Odvisno "
"od vaših nastavitev (glejte <xref linkend=\"subversion-settings\" xreflabel="
"\"settings\"/>) &kdesvn; pridobi nekaj dnevniških vnosov, ki se začnejo na "
"<quote>HEAD</quote>, in jih prikaže."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid "The log display dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno za prikaz dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left side you see the list of log entries retrieved by &kdesvn;. The "
"log message is stripped-down to one line to fit. The full log message "
"appears in the upper-right window when marking an entry. In the lower-right "
"window you will see the list of changed files. These windows <emphasis>only</"
"emphasis> appear if this list is fetched, depending on your settings."
msgstr ""
"Na levi strani vidite seznam vnosov v dnevnik, ki jih je pridobil &kdesvn;. "
"Dnevniško sporočilo je skrajšano na eno vrstico, da se prilega. Ob "
"označevanju vnosa se v zgornjem desnem oknu prikaže celotno sporočilo "
"dnevnika. V spodnjem desnem oknu boste videli seznam spremenjenih datotek. "
"Ta okna se prikažejo <emphasis>samo</emphasis>, če je ta seznam pridobljen, "
"odvisno od vaših nastavitev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:337
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the buttons on the top you may select another range of logs to display."
msgstr "Z gumbi na vrhu lahko izberete drug obseg dnevnikov za prikaz."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This range is called without any pre-limit, so be careful when using this "
"feature on large repositories."
msgstr ""
"Ta obseg se kliče brez predhodne omejitve, zato bodite previdni pri uporabi "
"te funkcije v velikih repozitorijih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The buttons on the bottom of the dialog always work on the item selected for "
"log, not on the item selected in the list of changed files. So when you "
"select <guibutton>Diff previous</guibutton> there, it makes the diff over "
"all changed items in this revision if they are equivalent or below the "
"subversion entry selected before for retrieving logs. Same for "
"<guibutton>Diff revisions</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Gumbi na dnu pogovornega okna vedno delujejo na elementu, izbranem za "
"dnevnik, ne na elementu, izbranem na seznamu spremenjenih datotek. Torej, ko "
"tam izberete <guibutton>Razlik pred prejšnjim</guibutton>, naredi razliko "
"med vsemi spremenjenimi postavkami v tej reviziji, če so enakovredne ali pod "
"vnosom v subversion, izbranim prej za pridobivanje dnevnikov. Enako za "
"<guibutton>Revizije razlik</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guibutton>Annotate</guibutton> of course works only if item to log is a "
"file."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>Opomba</guibutton> seveda deluje samo, če je element, ki ga "
"želite prijaviti, datoteka."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On all list entries (both lists) you have context menu enabled for some "
"extra operations. In left list this is <guimenuitem>Set version as left side "
"of diff</guimenuitem> (&ie; beginning revision) and <guimenuitem>Set version "
"as right side of diff</guimenuitem> (&ie; end or target of diff, in unified "
"the part marked with a <computeroutput>+++</computeroutput>). If you "
"selected these revisions them are marked with some small arrows."
msgstr ""
"Na vseh vnosih seznama (oba seznama) imate omogočen kontekstni meni za "
"nekatere dodatne operacije. Na levem seznamu je to <guimenuitem>Nastavi "
"različico kot levo stran diff</guimenuitem> (&ie; začetna revizija) in "
"<guimenuitem>Nastavi različico kot desno stran diff</guimenuitem> (&ie; "
"konec ali cilj diff, v poenotil del, označen z <computeroutput>+++</"
"computeroutput>). Če ste izbrali te revizije, so označene z majhnimi "
"puščicami."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working on repositories"
msgstr "Delo na repozitorijih"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simple repository browsing may be done within &konqueror;, &dolphin; or "
"similar file browsers: Open a URL with protocol described in <xref linkend="
"\"kdesvn-features\" xreflabel=\"Features\"/> (the variants starting with "
"<quote>k</quote>) and them will display the content. So simple operations "
"like copy, move and delete may work. When appending a query <quote>?"
"rev=<replaceable>xxx</replaceable></quote> the listing comes from a specific "
"revision. Format of revision-query is described in <xref linkend=\"revision-"
"syntax\"/>, some more information about KIO::ksvn are in <xref linkend="
"\"kdesvn-kio\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Preprosto brskanje po repozitoriju lahko opravite v &konqueror;, &dolphin; "
"ali podobni brskalnikih datotek: odprite URL s protokolom, opisanim v <xref "
"linkend=\"kdesvn-features\" xreflabel=\"Features\"/> (različice, ki se "
"začnejo z <quote>k</quote>), in prikazali bodo vsebino. Tako lahko delujejo "
"preproste operacije, kot so kopiranje, premikanje in brisanje. Pri dodajanju "
"poizvedbe <quote>?rev=<replaceable>xxx</replaceable></quote> seznam izvira "
"iz določene revizije. Format revizijske poizvedbe je opisan v <xref linkend="
"\"revision-syntax\"/>, nekaj več informacij o KIO::ksvn je v <xref linkend="
"\"kdesvn-kio\"/>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All work except <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> may only done when browsing "
"at revision HEAD."
msgstr ""
"Vsa dela, razen <guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem>, se lahko izvajajo samo "
"med brskanjem na reviziji HEAD."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restoring deleted items"
msgstr "Obnavljanje izbrisanih predmetov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In subversion restoring deleted items is a copy operation of item at "
"specific revision. So when you plan restoring view repository at revision "
"before item was deleted. Select <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Repository</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Select browse revision</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and enter the wanted revision. Now &kdesvn; "
"displays the content at this term. Mark the entry you want to restore, "
"select <menuchoice> <shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</"
"keycap></keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>General</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Copy</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice>. Inside the following dialog the target is always at HEAD "
"revision, the source is at revision you selected for browsing. Fill in the "
"path and click <guibutton>OK</guibutton> and copy starts. After successful "
"copy switch browsing back to HEAD revision and the restored item should "
"appear."
msgstr ""
"Pri programu subversion je obnavljanje izbrisanih elementov operacija "
"kopiranja elementa pri določeni reviziji. Ko torej načrtujete obnovitev "
"repozitorija pogleda pri reviziji, preden je bil element izbrisan. Izberite "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Repozitorij</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Izberite prebrskaj revizijo</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> in vnesite želeno revizijo. Zdaj &kdesvn; prikaže vsebino tega "
"izraza. Označite vnos, ki ga želite obnoviti, izberite <menuchoice> "
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Splošno</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kopiraj</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Znotraj naslednjega "
"pogovornega okna je cilj vedno na GLAVNI reviziji, vir je na reviziji, ki "
"ste jo izbrali za brskanje. Vnesite pot in kliknite <guibutton>V redu</"
"guibutton> in kopiranje se začne. Po uspešnem kopiranju preklopite brskanje "
"nazaj na GLAVNO revizijo in obnovljeni element bi se moral prikazati."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "Importing folders"
msgstr "Uvažanje map"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:388
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Due restrictions of subversion itself only folders, not single files, may "
"imported."
msgstr ""
"Zaradi omejitev samega programa subversion se lahko uvozijo samo mape, ne "
"posamezne datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "With drag and drop"
msgstr "Z povleci in spusti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark in any compatible file manager the folder you want to import and drag "
"it to the folder entry in &kdesvn; where you want to import it."
msgstr ""
"V katerem koli združljivem upravitelju datotek označite mapo, ki jo želite "
"uvoziti, in jo povlecite na vnos mape v &kdesvn; kamor ga želite uvoziti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select folder to import with directory-browser"
msgstr "Izberite mapo za uvoz z brskalnikom imenikov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mark the folder where you want to import a new folder. Then select "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>General</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Import folders into current</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> and "
"select your wanted folder."
msgstr ""
"Označite mapo, v katero želite uvoziti novo mapo. Nato izberite <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Splošno</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Uvozi mape v trenutno</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> in izberite "
"želeno mapo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Operations"
msgstr "Druge operacije"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:413
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge"
msgstr "Spoji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open repository or working copy, mark item you want to merge and select "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>General</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Merge</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. Enter in the following dialog "
"the values wanted. If opened from repository, source 1 and source 2 are "
"filled, when open from within working copy, target is filled with current "
"selected item. The handling of this parameter is a little bit different "
"between using the internal diff of subversion or an external merge-program "
"like &kdiff3;. The target must ALWAYS a local folder or file. You may switch "
"between external or internal merge with the check box <guilabel>Use external "
"merge</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Odprite repozitorij ali delovno kopijo, označite element, ki ga želite "
"združiti, in izberite <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Splošno</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Združi</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice>. V naslednje pogovorno okno vnesite želene vrednosti. Če se "
"odpre iz repozitorija, se izvor 1 in izvor 2 zapolnita, ko se odpre znotraj "
"delovne kopije, se cilj zapolni s trenutno izbrano postavko. Ravnanje s tem "
"parametrom je nekoliko drugačno pri uporabi notranje diff subversion ali "
"zunanjega programa za spajanje, kot je &kdiff3;. Cilj mora biti VEDNO "
"lokalna mapa ali datoteka. Med zunanjim in notranjim spajanjem lahko "
"preklapljate s potrditvenim poljem <guilabel>Uporabi zunanje spajanje</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Internal merge"
msgstr "Notranje spajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The meaning is exactly like from within subversion's own command line tool. "
"When source1 and source2 are equal, start and endrevision must different. If "
"sources aren't equal, start-revision is assigned to source1 and end-revision "
"to source2. The target MUST be a working copy otherwise subversion will send "
"an error message."
msgstr ""
"Pomen je natanko tak kot znotraj lastnega orodja ukazne vrstice subversion. "
"Ko sta vir1 in vir2 enaka, se morata začetna in končna revizija razlikovati. "
"Če viri niso enaki, je začetna revizija dodeljena viru1, končna revizija pa "
"viru2. Cilj MORA biti delovna kopija, sicer bo program subversion poslal "
"sporočilo o napaki."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "The check boxes have following meanings:"
msgstr "Potrditvena polja imajo naslednje pomene:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recursive"
msgstr "Rekurzivno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do all operations recursive when working with folders."
msgstr "Pri delu z mapami izvajajte vse operacije rekurzivno."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handle unrelated as related items"
msgstr "Nepovezane obravnavajte kot povezane elemente"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set, unrelated items will be diffed as if they were related. Otherwise "
"subversion will remove one side and add it on other side again."
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljeno, se bodo nepovezani elementi razlikovali, kot da bi bili "
"povezani. V nasprotnem primeru bo subversion odstranil eno stran in jo znova "
"dodal na drugo stran."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid "Force delete on modified/unversioned items"
msgstr "Vsili brisanje spremenjenih elementov/nerazličic"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:448
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If not set and merge would require deletion of an modified or unversioned "
"item the subversion merge fails. Otherwise this items will be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Če ni nastavljeno in bi spajanje zahtevalo brisanje spremenjene postavke ali "
"postavke brez različic, spajanje v subversion ne uspe. V nasprotnem primeru "
"bodo ti elementi izbrisani."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:454
#, no-c-format
msgid "Just dry run without modifications"
msgstr "Samo suhi tek brez sprememb"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If set, subversion sends only notifications what it would do but doesn't "
"modify the working copy."
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljeno, subversion pošilja le obvestila, kaj bi storila, vendar "
"ne spreminja delovne kopije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using external program for merge"
msgstr "Uporaba zunanjega programa za spajanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"See <xref linkend=\"diffmerge-settings\"/> for details how to setup the "
"external merge tool. &kdesvn; generates the command line as described there. "
"Before it does following:"
msgstr ""
"Glejte <xref linkend=\"diffmerge-settings\"/> za podrobnosti o nastavitvi "
"zunanjega orodja za spajanje. &kdesvn; ustvari ukazno vrstico, kot je tam "
"opisano. Preden naredi naslednje:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:471
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Assign start-revision as revision to source 1 and end-revision to source 2. "
"Then checks if them are different (path and/or revision). If yes, it is a "
"three-way merge otherwise a simple merge from source to target. If source 2 "
"is left empty it is a simple merge, too."
msgstr ""
"Dodeli začetno revizijo kot revizijo viru 1 in končno revizijo viru 2. Nato "
"preveri, ali sta različna (pot in/ali revizija). Če je odgovor pritrdilen, "
"gre za trosmerno spajanje, drugače pa preprosto spajanje od vira do cilja. "
"Če vir 2 pustimo prazen, gre tudi za preprosto spajanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:475
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make an export into temporary folder. If it is a simple merge only source 1 "
"at start-revision, otherwise both sources with their revisions. If item is a "
"file and not a folder then get the content at a specific revision."
msgstr ""
"Izvozite v začasno mapo. Če gre za preprosto spajanje samo vira 1 na začetni "
"reviziji, drugače pa oba vira s svojimi revizijami. Če je element datoteka "
"in ne mapa, dobite vsebino pri določeni reviziji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:480
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Generate the call to your external merge program as you setup in <link "
"linkend=\"diffmerge-settings\">Settings</link>. The error output will "
"displayed in log window so you may see what is going wrong (if something is "
"gone wrong)."
msgstr ""
"Generirajte klic svojemu zunanjemu programu združevanja, ko nastavite v "
"<link linkend=\"diffmerge-settings\">Nastavitve</link>. Izhod napake bo "
"prikazan v oknu dnevnika, da boste lahko videli, kaj gre narobe (če je šlo "
"kaj narobe)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In difference to internal merge target may a flat folder/file not under "
"version control because external tools do not care about it."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od cilja notranjega združevanja lahko ravna mapa/datoteka ni pod "
"nadzorom različic, ker zunanja orodja za to ne skrbijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:488
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If recursive is not set, the export is done as a flat export. Be care: when "
"doing this with working copies externals will <emphasis>not</emphasis> be "
"exported."
msgstr ""
"Če rekurzivno ni nastavljeno, se izvoz izvede kot ravni izvoz. Bodite "
"previdni: ko to počnete z delovnimi kopijami, zunanje <emphasis>ne</"
"emphasis> bodo izvožene."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resolving conflicts"
msgstr "Reševanje konfliktov"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdesvn; itself hasn't a module for resolving conflicts but you may use "
"external software from within &kdesvn;. In <xref linkend=\"extern-resolve-"
"setup\"/> is a description how to setup up this application."
msgstr ""
"&kdesvn; sam po sebi nima modula za reševanje sporov, vendar lahko uporabite "
"zunanjo programsko opremo znotraj &kdesvn;. V <xref linkend=\"extern-resolve-"
"setup\"/> je opis, kako nastaviti to aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When marking an item with status set to <quote>conflicted</quote> (you'll "
"see a red cross in listview on such items) you may select <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Resolve conflict</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. or from within "
"context menu <guimenuitem>Resolve conflict</guimenuitem> (only on conflicted "
"items) &kdesvn; now starts the program you setup (or the default one). After "
"finish this job you should mark item as resolved "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Subversion</guimenu><guisubmenu>Working copy</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Mark resolved</guisubmenu></menuchoice>) otherwise "
"you will not able to commit your changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko označujete element s statusom, nastavljenim na <quote>v sporu</quote> (na "
"takšnih elementih boste v pogledu seznama videli rdeč križec), lahko "
"izberete <menuchoice> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna "
"kopija</guisubmenu> <guisubmenu>Reši spor</guisubmenu> </menuchoice>. ali "
"znotraj kontekstnega menija <guimenuitem>Reši spor</guimenuitem> (samo pri "
"elementih v sporu) &kdesvn; zdaj zažene program, ki ste ga nastavili (ali "
"privzetega). Ko končate to opravilo, označite element kot razrešen "
"(<menuchoice><guimenu>Subversion</guimenu><guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</"
"guisubmenu><guisubmenu>Označi razrešeno</guisubmenu></menuchoice>), sicer ne "
"boste mogli da potrdite svoje spremembe."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid "Properties used by &kdesvn; for configuration"
msgstr "Lastnosti, ki jih uporablja &kdesvn; za konfiguracijo"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:517
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bugtracker integration"
msgstr "Integracija Bugtrackerja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <ulink url=\"http://tortoisesvn.tigris.org/\">TortoiseSVN project</"
"ulink> designed a nice property system <ulink url=\"http://tortoisesvn.net/"
"docs/release/TortoiseSVN_en/tsvn-dug-bugtracker.html\"> for integrating "
"bugtracker</ulink> into subversion GUI. The current version of &kdesvn; does "
"not support extra fields in commit box (will follow later) and doesn't "
"understand all but following properties:"
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"http://tortoisesvn.tigris.org/\">Projekt TortoiseSVN</ulink> je "
"oblikoval lep sistem lastnosti <ulink url=\"http://tortoisesvn.net/docs/"
"release/TortoiseSVN_en/tsvn- dug-bugtracker.html\"> za integracijo "
"sledilnika napak</ulink> v GUI subversion. Trenutna različica &kdesvn; ne "
"podpira dodatnih polj v polju za potrditev (bo sledilo kasneje) in ne razume "
"vseh razen naslednjih lastnosti:"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bugtracker Integration Properties"
msgstr "Lastnosti integracije Bugtrackerja"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Property"
msgstr "Lastnina"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "<entry>Description</entry>"
msgstr "<entry>Opis</entry>"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example"
msgstr "Primer"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "bugtraq:url"
msgstr "bugtraq:url"

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Holds the &URL; to bugtracker. It has to contain the <literal>%BUGID%</"
"literal> marker."
msgstr ""
"Vsebuje &URL; v sledilnik hroščev. Vsebovati mora oznako <literal>%BUGID%</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: entry
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid "https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=%BUGID%"
msgstr "https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=%BUGID%"

#. Tag: literal
#: index.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "bugtraq:logregex"
msgstr "bugtraq:logregex"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contains one or two regular expressions, separated by a newline."
msgstr "Vsebuje enega ali dva regularna izraza, ločena z novo vrstico."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If only one expression is set, then the bare bug ID's must be matched in the "
"groups of the regex string. If two expressions are set, then the first "
"expression is used to find a string which relates to the bug ID but may "
"contain more than just the bug ID (&eg; <quote>Issue #123</quote> or "
"<quote>resolves issue 123</quote>). The second expression is then used to "
"extract the bare bug ID from the string extracted with the first expression."
msgstr ""
"Če je nastavljen samo en izraz, se morajo goli ID-ji napak ujemati v "
"skupinah niza regularnega izraza. Če sta nastavljena dva izraza, se prvi "
"izraz uporabi za iskanje niza, ki se nanaša na ID hrošča, vendar lahko "
"vsebuje več kot samo ID hrošča (&eg; <quote>Težava #123</quote> ali "
"<quote>odpravlja težavo 123</quote>). Drugi izraz se nato uporabi za "
"ekstrahiranje golega ID-ja hrošča iz niza, ekstrahiranega s prvim izrazom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please keep care about not wanted spaces after the regular expression and "
"don't forget the brackets around the number description."
msgstr ""
"Pazite na nezaželene presledke za regularnim izrazom in ne pozabite na "
"oklepaje okoli opisa številke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "Single (usable with TRAC):"
msgstr "Eno (uporabno s TRAC):"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "#(\\d+)"
msgstr "#(\\d+)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:553
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now all numbers like <replaceable>#190</replaceable> will parsed and "
"translated to an &URL; in log output."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj bodo vse številke, kot je <replaceable>#190</replaceable>, razčlenjene "
"in prevedene v &URL; v izpisu dnevnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid "Two expressions:"
msgstr "Dva izraza:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[Ii]ssue #?(\\d+)(,? ?#(\\d+))*\n"
"(\\d+)"
msgstr ""
"[Ii]težava #?(\\d+)(,? ?#(\\d+))*\n"
"(\\d+)"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid "Remember"
msgstr "Ne pozabite"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep care of white spaces after the <literal>(\\d+)</literal>! This is one "
"of the most common errors causing these expressions do not match!"
msgstr ""
"Pazite na bele prostore za <literal>(\\d+)</literal>! To je ena "
"najpogostejših napak, zaradi katere se ti izrazi ne ujemajo!"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On local opened repositories (&ie; <filename class=\"directory\">file://</"
"filename> protocol) and on working copies these properties will searched "
"upward from opened folder until found or the subversion top level is "
"reached. On repositories opened via network (all except <filename class="
"\"directory\">file://</filename> protocol) it is only searched on opened "
"folder itself."
msgstr ""
"V lokalnih odprtih repozitorijih (&ie;. protokol <filename class=\"directory"
"\">file://</filename>) in na delovnih kopijah bodo te lastnosti iskale "
"navzgor od odprte mape, dokler ne bodo najdene ali dokler ni dosežena "
"najvišja raven programa subversion. V repozitorijih, odprtih prek omrežja "
"(vsi razen protokola <filename class=\"directory\">file://</filename>), se "
"išče le v sami odprti mapi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Support for multiple sets of these properties may follow later, (&eg;, in "
"subfolder extra values for other tracker &etc;) but in most cases evaluating "
"single tracker links should be enough."
msgstr ""
"Podpora za več nizov teh lastnosti lahko sledi pozneje (&eg; v podmapi "
"dodatne vrednosti za druge sledilnike &etc;), vendar bi v večini primerov "
"moralo zadostovati ocenjevanje povezav posameznega sledilnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid "The revision tree"
msgstr "Revizijsko drevo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The revision tree try to display the whole history of an item so user may "
"get a better feeling about the history of an item. It has to scan the "
"complete log of the repository 'cause it requires some information "
"subversion does not (and I think will not) give. Because this produces a lot "
"of traffic the revision tree uses always the internal <link linkend="
"\"logcache-descr\">log cache</link>."
msgstr ""
"Revizijsko drevo poskuša prikazati celotno zgodovino postavke, tako da lahko "
"uporabnik dobi boljši občutek o zgodovini postavke. Pregledati mora celoten "
"dnevnik repozitorija, ker zahteva nekaj informacij, ki jih subversion ne "
"daje (in mislim, da jih ne bo). Ker to povzroči veliko prometa, revizijsko "
"drevo vedno uporablja notranji <link linkend=\"logcache-descr"
"\">predpomnilnik dnevnika</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Zahteve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The revision tree is generated via <application>dot</application>. So for a "
"working revision tree the <application>graphviz</application> package must "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Revizijsko drevo se ustvari prek <application>pike</application>. Za "
"delujoče revizijsko drevo mora biti nameščen paket <application>graphviz</"
"application>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid "Internal log cache"
msgstr "Notranji predpomnilnik dnevnika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdesvn; may use an internal log cache for some operations. Mostly it is "
"used for <link linkend=\"revision-tree\">the revision tree</link> but when "
"viewing simplified log in offline mode, too. The caches are organized as "
"<application>SQLite</application> databases stored in <filename class="
"\"directory\">$HOME/.sqvnqt/logcache</filename>. Every numbered file is a "
"storage for a different repository."
msgstr ""
"&kdesvn; lahko za nekatere operacije uporablja notranji predpomnilnik "
"dnevnika. Večinoma se uporablja za <link linkend=\"revision-tree\">drevo "
"revizij</link>, vendar tudi pri ogledu poenostavljenega dnevnika v načinu "
"brez povezave. Predpomnilniki so organizirani kot zbirke podatkov "
"<application>SQLite</application>, shranjene v <filename class=\"directory\">"
"$HOME/.sqvnqt/logcache</filename>. Vsaka oštevilčena datoteka je shramba za "
"drugi repozitorij."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The databases may get large! So you may disable automatic update of log "
"cache in settings."
msgstr ""
"Baze podatkov lahko postanejo velike! Zato lahko v nastavitvah onemogočite "
"samodejno posodabljanje predpomnilnika dnevnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may simply remove a database, than no cached log will be given back for "
"that repository (and no revision tree!) but when you do not disable "
"automatic filling the cache on next open this repository or an associated "
"working copy of it the cache will be refilled again."
msgstr ""
"Bazo podatkov lahko preprosto odstranite, potem za ta repozitorij ne bo "
"vrnjen predpomnjeni dnevnik (in ne drevo revizij!), toda ko ne onemogočite "
"samodejnega polnjenja predpomnilnika ob naslednjem odprtju tega repozitorija "
"ali njegove povezane delovne kopije, bo predpomnilnik ponovno napolniti."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "Offline mode"
msgstr "Način brez povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:609
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdesvn; may work without network access, &ie; you can switch off the "
"network access for &kdesvn;. This may be useful when working without network "
"like on notebooks. In such cases &kdesvn; always gets the logs from the "
"internal cache. This log is reduced to base functions due to technical "
"reasons, so the cached log may (but not must) differ from real log. Differ "
"means that it will not display all copy operations even <guilabel>Log "
"follows node changes</guilabel> is set."
msgstr ""
"&kdesvn; lahko deluje brez dostopa do omrežja, &ie; lahko izklopite dostop "
"do omrežja za &kdesvn;. To je lahko uporabno pri delu brez omrežja, kot na "
"prenosnikih. V takih primerih &kdesvn; vedno dobi dnevnike iz notranjega "
"predpomnilnika. Ta dnevnik je zaradi tehničnih razlogov zmanjšan na osnovne "
"funkcije, zato se predpomnjeni dnevnik lahko (vendar ne mora) razlikovati od "
"pravega dnevnika. Različnost pomeni, da ne bo prikazal vseh operacij "
"kopiranja, tudi če je nastavljen <guilabel>Dnevnik sledi spremembam "
"vozlišča</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:612
#, no-c-format
msgid "Log cache and revision tree"
msgstr "Predpomnilnik dnevnika in drevo revizij"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The revision tree will only use the log cache because otherwise it must get "
"always the logs again. It will <emphasis>not</emphasis> refresh the log "
"cache (but this may changed in later releases)."
msgstr ""
"Revizijsko drevo bo uporabljalo samo predpomnilnik dnevnika, ker mora "
"drugače vedno znova dobiti dnevnike. <emphasis>Ne bo</emphasis> osvežil "
"predpomnilnika dnevnika (vendar se to lahko spremeni v kasnejših izdajah)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:620
#, no-c-format
msgid "Meaning of icon overlays"
msgstr "Pomen prekrivanja ikon"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries may be marked with overlayed icons when not in <quote>normal</quote> "
"state."
msgstr ""
"Vnosi so lahko označeni s prekritimi ikonami, če niso v <quote>normalnem</"
"quote> stanju."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Locked"
msgstr "Zaklenjeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This entry is locked. In last column the owner of lock is listed. You may "
"setup if &kdesvn; should check for locked items in repository, too. But be "
"careful: depending of the kind of the server this may take a long time!"
msgstr ""
"Ta vnos je zaklenjen. V zadnjem stolpcu je naveden lastnik ključavnice. "
"Nastavite lahko, če &kdesvn; bi moral preveriti tudi zaklenjene elemente v "
"repozitoriju. Vendar bodite previdni: odvisno od vrste strežnika lahko to "
"traja dolgo!"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:646
#, no-c-format
msgid "Needs locked"
msgstr "Potrebno zaklenjeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:650
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This entry must be locked before edit and commit. Until you'll not set a "
"lock subversion keeps it read-only."
msgstr ""
"Ta vnos mora biti zaklenjen pred urejanjem in objavo. Dokler ne nastavite "
"zaklepanja, subversion ostane samo za branje."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updates"
msgstr "Posodobitve"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:665
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This entry or - if a folder - an entry below has newer version in repository."
msgstr ""
"Ta vnos ali - če je mapa - spodnji vnos ima novejšo različico v repozitoriju."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:677
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modified"
msgstr "Spremenjeno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:681
#, no-c-format
msgid "This entry or - if a folder - an entry below was changed on local disc."
msgstr ""
"Ta vnos ali - če je mapa - spodnji vnos je bil spremenjen na lokalnem disku."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid "overlay added"
msgstr "dodana prekrivka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:696
#, no-c-format
msgid "This entry is locally added to subversion but not yet committed."
msgstr "Ta vnos je lokalno dodan v subversion, vendar še ni potrjen."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:707 index.docbook:722
#, no-c-format
msgid "overlay deleted"
msgstr "prekrivanje izbrisano"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This entry is locally deleted from subversion but hasn't yet been committed."
msgstr "Ta vnos je lokalno izbrisan iz subversion, vendar še ni bil potrjen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:726
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This entry (or entry below if folder) got conflicts to resolve with last "
"update."
msgstr ""
"Ta vnos (ali vnos spodaj, če je mapa) je dobil spore, ki jih je treba rešiti "
"z zadnjo posodobitvijo."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kdesvn; and passwords"
msgstr "&kdesvn; in gesla"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdesvn;/subversion is able to save passwords. Saving passwords is always a "
"security risk, but may let a graphical frontend more usable."
msgstr ""
"&kdesvn;/subversion lahko shranjuje gesla. Shranjevanje gesel je vedno "
"varnostno tveganje, vendar lahko omogoči večjo uporabnost grafičnega "
"vmesnika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:742
#, no-c-format
msgid "Not saving passwords"
msgstr "Gesla se ne shranjujejo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:743
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most secure way, but sometimes unhandy with GUIs like &kdesvn;. In "
"particular the background processes of &kdesvn; would always ask for a "
"password in case the repository has restricted access for reading operations "
"like update and status. The same for <quote>commit</quote> and so on. So if "
"you are not saving passwords you should disable <guilabel>Start check for "
"updates when open a working copy</guilabel> and <link linkend=\"subversion-"
"settings\">so on</link>."
msgstr ""
"Najbolj varen način, vendar včasih nepriročen z GUI-ji, kot je &kdesvn;. "
"Zlasti procesi v ozadju &kdesvn; bi vedno zahteval geslo, če ima repozitorij "
"omejen dostop za bralne operacije, kot sta posodobitev in stanje. Enako za "
"<quote>commit</quote> in tako naprej. Torej, če ne shranjujete gesel, "
"onemogočite <guilabel >Začni preverjanje posodobitev, ko odprete delovno "
"kopijo</guilabel> in <link linkend=\"subversion-settings\">tako naprej</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving passwords in &kwallet5;"
msgstr "Shranjevanje gesel v &kwallet5;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Secured password storage used by a lot of &kde; programs like &kmail; and "
"&konqueror;. If you are saving passwords and mostly using &kdesvn; you "
"should use this. Keep care that the encrypted storage isn't a high-secure "
"storage. Details see <ulink url=\"help:/kwallet5\">&kwallet5; documentation</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Zavarovano shranjevanje gesel, ki ga uporablja veliko &kde; programi, kot je "
"&kmail; in &konqueror;. Če shranjujete gesla in večinoma uporabljate "
"&kdesvn; to bi morali uporabiti. Pazite, da šifrirana shramba ni zelo varna "
"shramba. Podrobnosti glejte <ulink url=\"help:/kwallet5\">&kwallet5; "
"dokumentacija</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:754
#, no-c-format
msgid "Saving to subversion's own password storage"
msgstr "Shranjevanje v lastno shrambo gesel subversion"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is not recommended 'cause the passwords are stored as clear text! Not "
"believing? Take a look into the files in <filename class=\"directory\">~/."
"subversion/auth/svn.simple</filename>. You should only use this if you are "
"frequently using other clients than &kdesvn; like <application>rapidsvn</"
"application> or <application>esvn</application> or the original "
"<application>svn</application> command line client. If you're using the "
"command line client mostly for checkouts or updates which do not require a "
"password and &kdesvn; for commit/move/copy you should use &kwallet5; instead."
msgstr ""
"To ni priporočljivo, ker so gesla shranjena kot čisto besedilo! Ne verjameš? "
"Oglejte si datoteke v <filename class=\"directory\">~/.subversion/auth/svn."
"simple</filename>. To uporabite le, če pogosto uporabljate druge odjemalce "
"kot &kdesvn; kot je <application>rapidsvn</application> ali "
"<application>esvn</application> ali izvirni odjemalec ukazne vrstice "
"<application>svn</application>. Če odjemalca ukazne vrstice uporabljate "
"večinoma za nakupe ali posodobitve, ki ne zahtevajo gesla in &kdesvn; za "
"objavo/premaknitev/kopiranje uporabite &kwallet5; namesto tega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:760
#, no-c-format
msgid "Internal password cache"
msgstr "Notranji predpomnilnik gesel"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may activate an internal password cache which will hold passwords as "
"long &kdesvn; is running in memory. So you must not enter a password twice "
"even if you didn't save it in wallet."
msgstr ""
"Lahko aktivirate notranji predpomnilnik gesel, ki bo hranil gesla, dokler "
"&kdesvn; teče v pomnilniku. Torej ne smete dvakrat vnesti gesla, tudi če ga "
"niste shranili v denarnico."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid "Special case svn+ssh"
msgstr "Poseben primer svn+ssh"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:767
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using subversion via svn+ssh password storage may done via ssh and ssh-"
"agent. For this you must have ssh access to the remote machine and "
"repository. When want to store something you should use the public key "
"authentication of ssh, not the password authentication. (In fact ssh prefer "
"the public key authentication). For this you must put your public ssh-key on "
"the target, &eg;, the repository system. SSH passwords will never be handled "
"by subversion passwords storage or &kwallet5; or internal password cache."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi programa subversion prek svn+ssh lahko shranjevanje gesel "
"izvedete prek ssh in ssh-agenta. Za to morate imeti dostop ssh do "
"oddaljenega računalnika in repozitorija. Ko želite nekaj shraniti, morate "
"uporabiti avtentikacijo javnega ključa ssh, ne avtentikacije z geslom. "
"(Pravzaprav ima ssh raje avtentikacijo z javnim ključem). Za to morate "
"postaviti svoj javni ključ ssh na cilj, &eg;. sistem repozitorija. Gesla SSH "
"nikoli ne bodo obravnavana shrambo gesel subversion ali &kwallet5; ali "
"notranjega predpomnilnika gesel."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:770
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you don't want asked for the password of your SSH key you can use the "
"<application>ssh-agent</application>, with selecting the menu "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Subversion </guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add ssh identities "
"to ssh-agent</guimenuitem></menuchoice> you may store your SSH-key password "
"for your current session so no further entering of your password is needed."
msgstr ""
"Če ne želite, da vas vprašamo za geslo vašega ključa SSH, lahko uporabite "
"<application>ssh-agent</application> z izbiro menija <menuchoice><guimenu> "
"Subversion </guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj ssh identitete za ssh-agent</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> lahko shranite svoje geslo s ključem SSH za vašo "
"trenutno sejo, tako da vam ni potrebno nadaljnje vnašanje gesla."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:783
#, no-c-format
msgid "&konqueror;, KIO, &kdesvn;"
msgstr "&konqueror;, KIO, &kdesvn;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:785
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Description</title>"
msgstr "<title>Opis</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:786
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As of version 0.7.0 of &kdesvn; it comes with some modules integrating some "
"commands directly into &konqueror; menus."
msgstr ""
"Od različice 0.7.0 &kdesvn; prihaja z nekaterimi moduli, ki integrirajo "
"nekatere ukaze neposredno v &konqueror; meniji."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:790
#, no-c-format
msgid "KIO protocols"
msgstr "KIO protokoli"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:791
#, no-c-format
msgid "Implements handlers for the following protocols:"
msgstr "Implementira obdelovalce za naslednje protokole:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:793
#, no-c-format
msgid "ksvn+http"
msgstr "ksvn+http"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid "ksvn+https"
msgstr "ksvn+https"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:795
#, no-c-format
msgid "ksvn+file"
msgstr "ksvn+datoteka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:796
#, no-c-format
msgid "ksvn+ssh"
msgstr "ksvn+ssh"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "ksvn"
msgstr "ksvn"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:800
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These protocols are designed only for repositories, not for working copies. "
"For example, <filename class=\"directory\">ksvn+file:///<replaceable>path</"
"replaceable></filename> must point to the beginning of a repository "
"different to the application itself or KPart. Working copies may browsed "
"with &konqueror;."
msgstr ""
"Ti protokoli so zasnovani samo za repozitorije, ne za delovne kopije. Na "
"primer, <filename class=\"directory\">ksvn+file:///<replaceable>path</"
"replaceable></filename> mora kazati na začetek repozitorija, ki ni "
"aplikacija sama ali KPart. Delovne kopije lahko brskate s &konqueror;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For browsing at a specific revision you may append the query <link linkend="
"\"revision-syntax\"><quote>?rev=<replaceable>revision</replaceable></quote></"
"link> to the &URL;."
msgstr ""
"Za brskanje pri določeni reviziji lahko dodate poizvedbo <link linkend="
"\"revision-syntax\"><quote>?rev=<replaceable>revision</replaceable></quote></"
"link>na &URL;."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid "Context menus"
msgstr "Kontekstni meniji"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:811
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kdesvn; installs context menus for &konqueror;. Them may be seen with right "
"mouse click in the browser window (only in standard view, not any KPart) so "
"it is possible to do most used actions direct from within &konqueror; (or "
"any other file managers that read &konqueror; context menus like &dolphin;). "
"This is done via a call to the <link linkend=\"kdesvn-commandline\">command "
"line variant of &kdesvn;</link>."
msgstr ""
"&kdesvn; namesti kontekstne menije za &konqueror;. Ogledate si jih lahko z "
"desnim klikom miške v oknu brskalnika (samo v standardnem pogledu, ne v "
"katerem koli KPartu), tako da je mogoče večino uporabljenih dejanj izvajati "
"neposredno iz &konqueror;ja (ali katerega koli drugega upravljalnika "
"datotek, ki bere kontekstne menije &konqueror;, kot je &dolphin;). To se "
"izvede s klicem <link linkend=\"kdesvn-commandline\">različice ukazne "
"vrstice &kdesvn;</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:820
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage of KIO outside &konqueror; - an example"
msgstr "Uporaba KIO zunaj &konqueror;ja - primer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:821
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Every application which uses the KIO library may use these protocols. So it "
"would be possible to retrieve all differences between two revisions with "
"&kdiff3; without any deep knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka aplikacija, ki uporablja knjižnico KIO, lahko uporablja te protokole. "
"Tako bi bilo mogoče pridobiti vse razlike med dvema revizijama z &kdiff3; "
"brez globokega znanja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:826
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retrieving differences between revisions using &kdiff3; and KIO::ksvn"
msgstr "Pridobivanje razlik med revizijami z &kdiff3; in KIO::ksvn"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"kdiff3 \\\n"
"  ksvn://anonsvn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/arts?rev=423127 \\\n"
"  ksvn://anonsvn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/arts?rev=455064"
msgstr ""
"kdiff3 \\\n"
"  ksvn://anonsvn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/arts?rev=423127 \\\n"
"  ksvn://anonsvn.kde.org/home/kde/trunk/KDE/arts?rev=455064"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "Let &kdiff3; print all differences between two revisions."
msgstr "Naj &kdiff3; natisni vse razlike med dvema revizijama."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using this within &kdesvn; (diff'ing two revisions) is MUCH faster because "
"the internal mechanisms of subversion are used."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba tega znotraj &kdesvn; (razlikovanje dveh revizij) je VELIKO "
"hitrejši, ker se uporabljajo notranji mehanizmi programa subversion."

