"<member>Load dump into repository</member> </simplelist> For more "
"information please read the output of <command>svnadmin --help</command>"
msgstr ""
"Elementi menija z skrbniškimi nalogami za repozitorije subversion, kot so: "
"<simplelist> <member>Ustvari in odpri novo repozitorij</member> "
"<member>Prenesi repozitorij v datoteko</member> <member>Hotcopy repozitorij</"
"member> <member>Naloži dump into repository</member> </simplelist> Za več "
"informacij preberite izpis <command>svnadmin --help</command>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1775
#, no-c-format
