"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Add selected files/dirs</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>Vstavi</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj izbrane datoteke /dirs</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2008
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add selected files and/or folders to version control."
msgstr "Dodajte izbrane datoteke in/ali mape v nadzor različic."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Revert current changes</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Povrni trenutne spremembe</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2016
#, no-c-format
msgid "Revert changes made in working copy and updates to last updated state."
msgstr ""
"Povrni spremembe v delovni kopiji in posodobitve na zadnje posodobljeno "
"stanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Mark resolved</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Označi rešeno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2024
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mark conflicted items as not conflicted and remove associated files."
msgstr ""
"Označite konfliktne elemente kot nekonfliktne in odstranite povezane "
"datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Merge two revisions</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spoji dve reviziji</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2032
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge two revisions of entries into working copy."
msgstr "Spoji dve reviziji vnosov v delovno kopijo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Ignore/Unignore current item</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prezri/Odprezri trenutni element</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Edit property of parent folder of the current item so that selected item "
"will be marked as ignored if not set, otherwise remove it from ignore list."
msgstr ""
"Uredite lastnost nadrejene mape trenutnega elementa, tako da bo izbrani "
"element označen kot prezrt, če ni nastavljen, sicer ga odstranite s seznama "
"prezrtih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Cleanup</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Čiščenje</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2048
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clean up the working copy and remove (commit-)locks if any"
msgstr "Počistite delovno kopijo in odstranite (potrjene) ključavnice, če so"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Working copy</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Switch repository</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Delovna kopija</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preklopi repozitorij</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2056
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch the root of the current working copy."
msgstr "Preklopi koren trenutne delovne kopije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2061
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Repository</title>"
msgstr "<title>Repozitorij</title>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2063
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Repository</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Checkout current repository path</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Repozitorij</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Preveri trenutno pot repozitorija</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2068
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a working copy from the current selected entry if a directory."
msgstr "Ustvari delovno kopijo iz trenutno izbranega vnosa, če je imenik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2071
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Repository</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Export current repository path</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Repozitorij</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izvoz trenutne poti repozitorija</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2076
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a clean copy on local file system from the current selected entry if "
"a directory."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari čisto kopijo v lokalnem datotečnem sistemu iz trenutno izbranega "
"vnosa, če je imenik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2081
#, no-c-format
msgid "View actions"
msgstr "Ogled dejanj"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Refresh view</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F5</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Osveži pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2088
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Refresh</action> the current status of all displayed items. This "
"will list each item asked for to be displayed at current status."
msgstr ""
"<action>Osveži</action> trenutno stanje vseh prikazanih elementov. To bo "
"navedlo vse elemente, ki so zahtevani za prikaz v trenutnem stanju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2093
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Unfold File Tree / Fold File Tree</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Razgrni drevo datotek / Zloži drevo datotek</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2098
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand or collapse the repository tree view."
msgstr "Razširi ali strni drevesni pogled repozitorija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Log Cache</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Stop updating the log cache</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Predpomnilnik dnevnika</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Ustavi posodabljanje predpomnilnika dnevnika</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The log is cached and used to display the revision tree of a repository. "
"Depending on the Internet connection, size of the subversion repository and "
"history length this may take much time. Therefore you can stop updating the "
"cache using this action."
msgstr ""
"Dnevnik je predpomnjen in se uporablja za prikaz revizijskega drevesa "
"repozitorija. Odvisno od internetne povezave, velikosti subverzivnega "
"repozitorija in dolžine zgodovine lahko to traja veliko časa. Zato lahko s "
"tem dejanjem ustavite posodabljanje predpomnilnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Add ssh identities to ssh-agent</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Subversion</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodaj identitete ssh ssh-agentu</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Store your SSH-key password for your current session so no further entering "
"of your password is needed."
msgstr ""
"Shrani svoje geslo s ključem SSH za svojo trenutno sejo, tako da vam ni "
"potrebno nadaljnje vnašanje gesla."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2125
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Database Menu"
msgstr "Meni baze podatkov"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Database</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show database content</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Baza podatkov</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prikaži vsebino baze podatkov</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays an overview about the cache database content for known repositories "
"and allows to delete the cache or repository and access to repository "
"settings."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pregled vsebine baze podatkov predpomnilnika za znane repozitorije "
"in omogoča brisanje predpomnilnika ali repozitorija ter dostop do nastavitev "
"repozitorija."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:2137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Database</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Settings for current repository</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Baza podatkov</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nastavitve za trenutni "
"repozitorij</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display a dialog to adapt the settings for the cache, logs and statistics."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži pogovorno okno za prilagajanje nastavitev za predpomnilnik, dnevnike "
"in statistiko."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2148
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Settings and Help Menu"
msgstr "Meni Nastavitve in pomoč"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</"
"guimenu> menu items described in the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
