#. Tag: trans_comment
#: index.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid "CREDIT_FOR_TRANSLATORS"
msgstr "<para>Prevod: Matjaž Jeran <email>matjaz.jeran@amis.net</email></para>"

#. Tag: chapter
#: index.docbook:2247
#, no-c-format
msgid "&underFDL; &underGPL;"
msgstr "&underFDL; &underGPL;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Syntax for revisions"
msgstr "Sintaksa za revizije"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Revisions may be given in the same form as for the standard "
"<application>svn</application> client. That means: number, keyword or date."
msgstr ""
"Revizije so lahko podane v enaki obliki kot za standardnega odjemalca "
"<application>svn</application>. To pomeni: številka, ključna beseda ali "
"datum."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Številka"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A number greater or equal -1. -1 means <quote>unspecified revision</quote>, "
"0 is the beginning. Normally, these numbers should not be used (most "
"operations will fail with that)."
msgstr ""
"Število, večje ali enako -1. -1 pomeni <quote>nedoločeno revizijo</quote>, 0 "
"je začetek. Običajno teh številk ne bi smeli uporabljati (večina operacij s "
"tem ne uspe)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyword"
msgstr "Ključna beseda"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2270
#, no-c-format
msgid "One of"
msgstr "Eden od"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2274
#, no-c-format
msgid "HEAD"
msgstr "HEAD (GLAVA)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2278
#, no-c-format
msgid "BASE"
msgstr "BASE (BAZA)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2282
#, no-c-format
msgid "COMMITED"
msgstr "COMMITED (POTRJEN)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2286
#, no-c-format
msgid "PREV"
msgstr "PREV"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2290
#, no-c-format
msgid "START"
msgstr "START"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2294
#, no-c-format
msgid "WORKING"
msgstr "WORKING (DELOVNI)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keywords are case sensitive! For example, head is not the same as HEAD."
msgstr ""
"Ključne besede razlikujejo med velikimi in malimi črkami! Na primer, glava "
"ni isto kot GLAVA."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Date in form {YYYY-MM-DD}. It must real MM or DD - &eg; 2005-1-1 must be "
"written as {2005-01-01}."
msgstr ""
"Datum v obliki {LLLL-MM-DD}. Mora biti pravi MM ali DD - &eg; 2005-1-1 mora "
"biti zapisano kot {2005-01-01}."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Appending a specific revision to an &URL; will always made via <quote>?"
"rev=<replaceable>revision</replaceable></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje določene revizije &URL; bo vedno narejen prek <quote>?"
"rev=<replaceable>revizije</replaceable></quote>."
